<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>Lower left side of a <rs type="material">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType">block</rs> moulded below (c <measure dim="width" type="length" unit="metre">0.70</measure> x <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.42</measure> x <measure precision="circa" dim="depth" type="length" unit="metre">0.64</measure>).</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p><rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> on the visible face (a) within a moulded panel, and (b) on the lower moulding. There was already a faulty area on the face which the cutter avoided.
</p>
</div>
<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Letters</head>
<p>Ave. <measure dim="height" type="length" unit="metre">0.015</measure>. The serifs are exaggerated, but the forms not quite standard II - III cent.</p>
</div>
